 <span data-ttu-id="9e7df-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> é associado pelas restrições de segurança a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] aplicativo que está hospedando o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9e7df-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is bound by the security constraints of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application that is hosting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="9e7df-109">Quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> é hospedado por uma confiança total [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] (um aplicativo autônomo, por exemplo), do aplicativo <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> pode hospedar [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documentos de qualquer local.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9e7df-109">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a full-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (a stand-alone application, for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documents from any location.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="9e7df-110">Quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> é hospedado por um de confiança parcial [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] aplicativo (um [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], por exemplo), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> só pode hospedar os documentos são **Site de origem** arquivos de dados do aplicativo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9e7df-110">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a partial-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can only host documents that are **Site Of Origin** application data files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9e7df-111">Para mais informações, consulte [Arquivos de recurso, conteúdo e dados do aplicativo WPF](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9e7df-111">For more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md).</span></span>  
  
